column6: Fish got away, before recording tag, but a recap.

Not sure if we should keep or toss.  There was no secondary fin clip, but a needle was found in the fish.  I kinda sorta remember someone mentioning that this happened, but don't remember who or where.
Fish is <250 mm.  Should we keep or toss since objective is at least 250 mm.  Thinking toss.  This is the only outlier.
Saw tag wound, but no fin clip.  I'd say toss.
No tag, but left fin clip, so a recapture
